snippet.title: Maestro VR - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Maestro VR is a rhythmic music video game where you become an orchestra conductor in Virtual Reality. Feel the unique experience of conducting a symphony orchestra.

Early Access begins on November 4th on Steam.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1327920/Maestro_VR
https://maestrovr.com

#MaestroVR #Maestro_VR #OrchestraVR
